reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Easy to hang
reviews.reviewText: This was easy to hang so no issues there. I guess the main issue I have is that it doesn't get as tight as I would like. There is still a bit of a wiggle at the smallest setting. It does the job though and for the price I would recommend it. I used this to hang a Verizon cable box.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Worked perfect to mount my modem on the wall
reviews.reviewText: I was very pleased with this little mounting bracket. I was able to put my modem on the wall next to my router. The depth was adjustable so I was able to make sure it was nice and secure. I highly recommend this product.
